<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Asti śrīmati matsyavaṁśavipulakṣīrāṁbudhā <gap reason="lost" quantity="2" unit="character"/> yō jātō vīraja
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yaṁtaśītakiraṇaḥ pūrnnaḥ kaḷāsaṁpadā tasyāpīt bhuvi rōhiṇīva ramaṇī khyātā gu
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṇaiściṁgamā dēvī sā patirājyavaibhavakṛtē svābhīṣṭasaṁsiddhayē <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">1</supplied> śākābdhē śītaraśmikṣitidharadinakṛt
<lb n="4" break="no"/>sammitē śuklapakṣē kanyārkkē jīvavārē bhujagapatitidhau śrīnṛsiṁhasya bhaktyā <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> dattvākhaṁḍaṁ sadaṁḍaṁ
<lb n="5"/>ta<unclear>ra</unclear>ṇikaranibhaṁ prājyamājyēna dīpaṁ tatsaṁtā<supplied reason="omitted">nā</supplied>ya paṁcchāśatamapi tadanu prādadānnaicikīnāṁ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">2</supplied>
<lb n="6"/>Ācaṁdratārakaṁ dharmmaṁ tamimannirmmalāśayāḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> viṣṇukarmmasu niṣṇātāḥ pālayaṁtvi
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ha vaiṣṇavāḥ <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> <supplied reason="omitted">3</supplied> śrīśakavaruṣaṁbulu 1271 gunēṁṭi Āśvayuja vimala paṁcchamiyu
<lb n="8"/>guruvāramunāṁḍu Oḍḍavādi jayaṁtikadēvarājula mahādēvi mahārāju ciṁgamadēvi ta
<lb n="9" break="no"/>naku nabhīṣṭasidhdhigānu śrīnarasiṁhanāthuni sannidhiyaṁdu nittyamunnu Akhaṁḍadīpamu ve
<lb n="10" break="no"/>luṁguṭakuṁ beṭṭina mōdālu 50 dīpapratima Okaṁḍu Ī dharmmu Ācaṁdrārkkasthāyigā
<lb n="11" break="no"/>ṁ jallaṁgaladi <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatruṇāpi kṛtō dharmmaḥ pālanīyō manīṣibhiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatrurēva hi śatru<unclear>ḥ</unclear>syāt
<lb n="12"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="1" unit="character"/> <unclear>dha</unclear>rmma śśatrurnna kasyacit <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī dharmmupu śrīvaiṣṇava rakṣa <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrīśrīśrī <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> Ī mōdālu cittarāma
<lb n="13" break="no"/>hōmmusēnā<note n="383-1">nā is entered below the line.</note>patinni tammanasēnāpati tammuṁḍu ciṁgana<unclear>ya</unclear>ṇi <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> bhaṁḍārā
<lb n="14" break="no"/>nanu pravēśamucēyanu tammanasēnāpati pūṁṭa <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
<lb n="15"/> <gap reason="lost" quantity="10" unit="character"/> 
</p>

